      "text": [
        " اَللَّهُ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ «يَا اِبْنَ آدَمَ اُذْكُرْنِي بَعْدَ اَلْغَدَاةِ سَاعَةً وَ بَعْدَ اَلْعَصْرِ سَاعَةً أَكْفِيكَ مَا أَهَمَّكَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.965 - The Prophet (sw) said that Allah (swt) the Almighty said:\n\"O’ son of Adam, remember Me for an hour after the dawn (fajr) prayer and for an hour after the afternoon (Asr) prayer, and I will take care of what concerns you.\""
        ]
      }
